title: For Sale:  Accuracy International AX308 Rifle
postcontent:
The AX308 sniper rifle from Accuracy International inherited the best features of the Accuracy International AW series rifles and improved on many others.
Fixed butt pads are standard with target adjustable and quick adjust butt pads optionally available. The trigger is an adjustable two stage mechanism that allows a large sear engagement until the first stage is taken up. The rifle has a three position safety mechanism. The safety will only operate when the bolt is cocked. The 20mm diameter steel close fitting bolt features an integral short throw bolt handle (60°) with large bolt knob which lies close to the stockside just above the trigger. The bolt can be field stripped without tools for cleaning.
The AX308 action uses a double stack 10 round magazine. Magazine Surfaces are toughened and finished with a multi-part anti-corrosive, anti-friction coating. This military grade steel magazine combined with the revised chassis design makes loading faster and more positive without lifting the rifle. The Accuracy International AX308 forend rail system is free floating in either 16" or 13" featuring a keyhole slot system for quickly and securely attaching modular rail sections. Full length picatinny rails in flat, 20 MOA or 30 MOA options match the action rail.No Trade.

postcontent:
This is a 37 mm launcher reloading kit that will load any 37 mm flare or smoke grenade shells. BATF rules say this system is completely legal for civilian use as
long as you do not use it for high explosive or gas projectiles.
It comes in a Hardigg hard case which can double as a handgun carry case.
Charges or shells are not included from the manufacturer but they are available from many sources. If you can find one these kits go for over $600.
With it is a CM203 Cobray 37 mm launcher designed after the military 40 mm M203. There are some differences such as a charging handle, while the M203 cocks when you close it and a safety switch which the M203 does not have. Otherwise they mount and operate much the same. Again this is perfectly legal according to BATF and are not even considered firearms. They are classed as flare launchers.
These will mount not only on the AR15 platform but other rifle systems as well with
the correct rail system, such as the AK47.
Both items are like new but used. There is a small amount of non-pitting corrosion on the housing above the trigger housing and a prior owner had applied a bead of epoxy
along the top of the forgrip. Ten minutes with a dremel will make it disappear. The reloader is missing the tube cleaner nylon bristle brush but you can substitute a baby
bottle brush.
Together these two items retail for over $1000. I will sell them to the highest
offer over $500. I will accept US currency, Paypal, metals, ammo or guns in trade and will exchange FTF in NC or ship them to you.

A micrometer adjuster that reads directly in cubic centimeters. Just multiply the charge in grains by the cc for one grain and you have the setting. So very much better than a meaningless setting as most supply.

Versatile:
The metering chamber is the proper size for large rifle charges and the strike off opening small enough to work well with pistol size charges. The Lee Perfect Powder Measure works fine for charges from two grains to over 100 grains.

970-797-2397
